sirrus corp
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Staples
Industry: Consumer Products
Sub-Industry: Tobacco
Sirrus Corp. designs, manufactures, and markets electronic cigarettes. The Company distributes electronic cigarettes in East Africa.




